{"build_type":"library","description":"Concise lens: walk a function body / branch body as a json-tree-node linked list (node = first instruction, follow .next), concise-rendering each via vw_one_instruction into body_out. Native .child/.next traversal — no fetch_member_residing_within_sequence index counting (O(n^2) + NULL-deref source). Caller passes the first child (execution_instructions.child or a branch array's .child); 0 means empty body. Tail-recursive on .next. Reuses vw_one_instruction, append_element_extending_document_sequence.","module_name":"render-concise-representation-across-instruction-block","package_name":"render-concise-representation-across-instruction-block","function_definitions":{"render-concise-representation-across-instruction-block":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"node","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"body_out","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"node"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"render-concise-single-instruction-statement","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"node"}],"result_assignment_variable":"res","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"append-element-extending-document-sequence","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"body_out"},{"kind":"var","value":"res"}]},{"instruction_type":"field_read","struct":"json-tree-node","field":"next","base":"node","dest":"nxt"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"render-concise-representation-across-instruction-block","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"nxt"},{"kind":"var","value":"body_out"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}